Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.00,0:03:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1\fs18\fnMonotype Corsiva}bbs.cnseikai.com
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.00,0:03:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1\fs18}特别鸣谢：幻炎28分舰队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.00,0:03:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1\fs18}压制：alex
